        <heading xml:lang="en-NZ">Governor-General's warrant for issue of writ: indicative referendum not conducted by postal voting</heading>
        <prov.body/>
        <notes>
          <history>
            <history-note id="DLM318613">Sections <amended-provision>24</amended-provision>, <amended-provision>25</amended-provision>, <amended-provision>26</amended-provision> and <amended-provision>26A</amended-provision> were <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, as from <amendment-date>15 November 2000</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM75008">section 88</amending-provision> <amending-leg>Referenda (Postal Voting) Act 2000</amending-leg> (2000 No 48).</history-note>
