            </para>
            <para>
              <text>Pursuant to section 26 of the Citizens Initiated Referenda Act 1993, I authorise and require <insertwords>the Electoral Commission to</insertwords> make all necessary arrangements for the conduct of an indicative referendum on the following question, namely, [<emphasis style="italic">specify the question</emphasis>].</text>
